description: Offers due Tues 6/24 - 5PM Welcome to 8 Story Street! Nestled on a peaceful street in the beautiful Thomas Park neighborhood, this spacious bi-level row house blends comfort, convenience, and coastal charm. Featuring 3 bedrooms, 1 full bath, and a versatile bonus room ideal for a home office or gym, this home is move-in ready with plenty of room to grow.Step outside to your private back deck and patio oasis—perfect for relaxing or entertaining.Just minutes from the beach, grocery stores, restaurants,Seaport, Downtown, and public transportation, you’ll enjoy easy access to everything you need. The neighborhood’s quiet charm, combined with unmatched convenience, creates a rare and inviting lifestyle opportunity.Whether you’re a homeowner or investor seeking strong long-term value, 8 Story Street offers tremendous upside potential in one of the area’s most desirable communities.
